last_restarted_at.description:
LastRestartedAt records when the last reboot was initiated by the controller.

This is set to `spec.restart_requested_at` when the controller processes a restart request.
It will be empty if no reboot has been performed yet.

Example (when converted to JSON):

   {
     "status": {
       "state": "COMPUTE_INSTANCE_STATE_READY",
       "last_restarted_at": "2026-01-20T14:30:00Z"
     }
   }

